    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK455">
<l>maṉattūymai ceyviṉai tūymai yiraṇṭu</l>
<l>miṉantūymai tūvā varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Chaste company is the staff on which come, these two things, viz, purity of mind and purity of conduct.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
